# Bhumisetu – Land & Environmental Intelligence Platform

Bhumisetu is a Land and Environmental Intelligence Platform focused on developing systems for understanding land ecosystems, environmental dynamics and sustainable infrastructure planning.

The platform aims to support responsible land governance, ecological balance and environmental intelligence through advanced technologies and research frameworks.

## Focus Areas

- Land intelligence systems
- Environmental monitoring
- Ecological balance analytics
- Sustainable infrastructure planning
- Environmental data intelligence

